Posts.Content: Hi Ladies, Have any of you had the OncotypeDX test?  I had it done and my score was a 9 so I didn't take chemo.  I had a lump with rads and tamoxifen.  I'm really curious if any of you had the test and scored low but got cancer back anyway.  Thanks for your input!!
Posts.Title: OncotypeDX test

Posts.Content: I believe my breast cancer was caused by a combination of things: 1. Took BC pills for 19 years 2. Drank alcohol socially on weekends 3. Drank caffeine 4. Ate red meat 5 or more times a week 5. Ate lots of white pasta and bread.  I no longer do any of the above and hope that I can keep cancer from coming back.  Good luck to all of you!!
